	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi quidem tuas, chare frater, literas una cum excerptis causae <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l646">Claronensis</placeName>; sed nunc, quod scribam, non habeo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sequestres dominica reminiscere <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l300">Lucernam</placeName> ibunt, inde ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l781">Urianos</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2450">Svytenses</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2469">Subsylvanos</placeName>, tentaturi, num possint ab his impetrare, ut consentiant in pacem sicuti Lucernates et Togeni.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Faxit dominus, ut omnia feliciter ad gloriam dei et pacem nostram cedant ad salutem animarum!</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fama est 23. februarii in aulam regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464">Galliae</placeName> perventurum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l691">Lotharingum</placeName> cardinalem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod si verum est, nihil mihi vel boni vel pacis polliceor.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Erynnis</persName> et furia infernalis est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc nunc me consolatur, quod dominus noster et diaboli est dominus, qui et momento potest alastores illos tollere e medio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Recte ille gerit purpuram, qui totus sanguine innoxio conspersus, imo complutus est statque in cruore fidelium usque ad collum, imo supra caput.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name">Thomyris</persName> aliqua dominum usqueadeo cruentum, reverendum dicere volebam, pro dignitate tractare posset.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum iudicia dei sunt, qui iustus est et verax.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vix dixero, quanto tenear desyderio videndi sessionem 9. et conclusionis concilii.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vellicabis ergo aurem omnibus, a quibus aliquid speras.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die 60000 duggaten werdent verplumpen in den unersettigen gmuͤten wie ein ply klotz imm <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2528">Bodensee</placeName> etc.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri 18. februarii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui fit, quod <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4037">Zanchus</persName> ne<foreign xml:lang="el">γρθ</foreign> quidem scribit?</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non suspicaris alibi apud <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648">Rhetos</placeName> latere <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2336">Ochinum</persName>; quo pervenerit scire non possum.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te mei omnes.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="manual">1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioanni Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro, domino meo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
